## 📁 Project Structure

```
PORTOFOLIO/
├── src/
│   ├── components/
│   │   ├── Navbar.jsx      # Glassmorphism navbar + theme toggle
│   │   ├── Hero.jsx        # Particle effects + typed animation
│   │   ├── About.jsx       # Animated stats
│   │   ├── Skills.jsx      # Progress bars
│   │   ├── Projects.jsx    # 3D hover cards
│   │   ├── Contact.jsx     # Animated form
│   │   └── Footer.jsx      # Heart animation
│   ├── App.jsx
│   ├── index.css           # Complete design system
│   └── main.jsx
├── index.html
├── package.json
└── vite.config.js
```

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

| Technology | Purpose |
|------------|---------|
| **React + Vite** | Fast development & build |
| **Framer Motion** | Smooth animations |
| **React Type Animation** | Typed text effect |
| **React Icons** | Icon library |

---

## 🚀 How to Run

```bash
cd PORTOFOLIO
npm run dev
```

Buka **http://localhost:5173** di browser.

---

